24.title: Activate display advertising features based on condition

ef260e9aa3c673af240d17a2660480361a8e081d.name: dev
ef260e9aa3c673af240d17a2660480361a8e081d.code:
/**
 * Scope       : Google Analytics (gtag.js)
 * 
 * Condition   : A consent-based condition should be added, this should only fire when the user has consented to 
 *               this specific kind of advertising / remarketing.
 * 
 * Description : Activate Google's 'Display Advertising Features' conditionally, based on a separate consent requirement,
 *               than the one required to fire the Google Analytics tag in general (advertising vs analytics).
 *
 */ 

u.data.allow_display_features = 'true'
u.data.config.allow_display_features = 'true'
u.data.config.allow_ad_personalization_signals = 'true'
u.data.config.allow_google_signals = 'true'
